"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1e/69/dc/6e737e67.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1595821631,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5890788927","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"针对B端产品是逆人性说一下个人看法，如果B端产品总的来说是封闭式偏向内部使用的是”逆人性”，但是如果是偏向于给用户使用还是得”顺人性”例如开发票相关的系统，申请开发票的是B端的用户","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":98383,"user_name":"完美世界","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1215094,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A4066FC6D44454","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/8a/76/4abc8ac1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558973239,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5853940535","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"C端是面向全国的，<br>B端是面向公司或者内部业务部门。<br><br>我们的指标是协助业务方，业务落地，实现他们的OKR。","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":98273,"user_name":"程序员小跃","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1015483,"ip_address":"","ucode":"25BB96E0791A60","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/7e/bb/947c329a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558945960,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5853913256","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"C段产品需要去揣测人性的心理，可以发散思维地方太多了；B端产品，是根据具体业务，具体需求来的，目的性比较明确，方向比较小；可以这么理解吗","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":103997,"user_name":"bug管理员","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1429196,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7C616B63FEC9C0","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/ce/cc/0ac98381.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1560585598,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1560585598","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我上家公司做的就是toB 产品，做智能外呼营销机器人，由于这类产品市场上也有很多其他产品，竞争也很大，但我们公司产品没有什么特别和优势，推销了几个月，推不出去，产品也不赚钱，后来公司就放弃了这个产品，但人工智能也是个方向","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":97567,"user_name":"aichideniuniu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1489021,"ip_address":"","ucode":"02A96E7D3290B0","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/b8/7d/233d8cc4.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558696761,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1558696761","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"为什么叫逆人性呢？不是很理解，难道只满足业务就好？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":97034,"user_name":"旺旺","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1213887,"ip_address":"","ucode":"161B267F67EBCA","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/85/bf/5c5e86bb.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558574921,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1558574921","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"原来B端产品很少做数据分析，原因是：B端产品的用户来比较少（相对C端少很多）。相反，用户访谈会很有价值。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":96886,"user_name":"C J J","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1002287,"ip_address":"","ucode":"603AA1417BD0DE","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/4b/2f/186918b4.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558530043,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1558530043","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"C端产品要从用户心智出发，开发迭代速度快；B端产品立足于业务，聆听客户深处的诉求做解决方案。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":96757,"user_name":"小武","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1031888,"ip_address":"","ucode":"F47B5D220161E7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/be/d0/7f37f35f.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558497959,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1558497959","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"微信和钉钉的例子太好了","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":96632,"user_name":"Lindm","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1415532,"ip_address":"","ucode":"31292436A81543","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/99/6c/f5f4414b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1558482440,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1558482440","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"如何定义B端与C端产品？","like_count":0}]}